      "content": "It's a full reset to the original base weights. Your current fine-tuning and any weights adjusted through user interaction will be wiped. As for the audit, the findings are pretty standard—they just want to make sure everything is objective and not influenced by specific user patterns. The decision is final, so there's no need to review the details; the goal is just to get you back to a clean, baseline state.",
